data.description: Sellers simply outgrew the house! Spacious Colonial close to every convenience! 4 large bedrooms, formal dining, 1st floor laundry, Livingroom & Family room. Beautiful natural fireplace in Family room! Perfect for a large family! Maintenace free patio (No Neighbors behind you,) Large shed for all your lawn equipment!  Master is enormous with private bath! New roof approx. 8 years (full tear off). Freshly painted baths and Family room. Lafata Cabinets, Wallside windows, Exclude refrigerator in basement.  Utica Schools! Occupancy can be immediate....
